data.description: Beautifully remodeled kitchen cabinets and countertops accentuate this 3-bedroom home featuring single-level living and a delightful open concept floorplan.  Located just blocks from Price City Downtown Main Street and conveniently placed near South Park. Central Air Conditioning, Shed, dishwasher and more.  Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from public record.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
